---
import Layout from "@/layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | NodeFlux Pte. Ltd."
  description="Read the privacy policy of NodeFlux Pte. Ltd. to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal data in compliance with Singapore's PDPA regulations."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="space-y-12 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Privacy Policy of Nodeflux Pte. Ltd</h1>
      <p class="text-foreground/80">Last Updated: 8/Aug/2024</p>
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="space-y-5">
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            At <span class="font-semibold">Nodeflux Pte. Ltd</span> (hereinafter referred to as “we,” “our,” or “the Company”), we are fully
            committed to safeguarding and preserving the privacy of all individuals (hereinafter referred to as “you,” “your,” or “user”) who
            interact with us, whether by using our website, completing forms, or otherwise engaging with our services. This policy provides a
            comprehensive description of how we collect, use, retain, share, and protect your personal information in full compliance with the
            applicable legal frameworks, including but not limited to the <span class="font-semibold"
              >Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA)</span
            > of Singapore.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">1. Scope of This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            This Privacy Policy applies to all personal data collected by <span class="font-semibold">Nodeflux Pte. Ltd</span> from users of
            our digital platforms, websites, forms, or any other interaction point, regardless of the medium or technology utilized. This includes,
            but is not limited to, any form submissions, telephonic communications, email correspondences, and any other means by which we might
            collect personal data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. Personal Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We may collect, record, and process various categories of personal data provided by you, including but not limited to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-3 text-foreground/80">
            <li>Full Name: As per the details you voluntarily provide when completing our lead generation form.</li>
            <li>Email Address: Required for communication purposes.</li>
            <li>Phone Number: Provided to facilitate prompt follow-up by our sales team.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We emphasize that this data is collected only with your informed consent, typically given by means of an opt-in checkbox, which
            signifies your explicit agreement to be contacted by our team.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. How We Collect Your Personal Data</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">Personal data is collected directly from you via the following channels:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-3 text-foreground/80">
            <li>Form Submissions: When you voluntarily submit your details through our website form(s).</li>
            <li>
              Explicit Consent Mechanism: Your completion of the opt-in process is considered consent to the collection and use of your
              personal data.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">4. How We Use Your Personal Data</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">The personal data we collect is used to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-3 text-foreground/80">
            <li>Follow up on your inquiries and form submissions with relevant service information.</li>
            <li>Facilitate communication between you and our sales representatives.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">5. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We are committed to protecting your personal data and implement various security measures, such as encryption, access controls,
            and internal audits, to prevent unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">6. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We retain your personal data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy unless a longer
            retention period is required by law.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">7. Sharing of Personal Data</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We do not share your personal data with third parties, except where required by law or with your consent.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">8. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">As a data subject, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-3 text-foreground/80">
            <li>Right to Access: You may request access to the personal data we hold about you.</li>
            <li>Right to Rectification: You may request corrections to inaccurate or incomplete personal data.</li>
            <li>Right to Withdraw Consent: You may withdraw your consent to the use of your personal data at any time.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">9. Data Security Measures</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We take appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect personal data, including encryption, access controls, and
            internal audits. However, we cannot guarantee absolute security, and we advise you to take precautions when interacting with us
            online.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">10. Data Breach Response</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            Although we do not currently have a formal data breach protocol, we take data breaches seriously. In the event of a breach
            involving your personal data, we will promptly mitigate the breach and notify affected individuals as per PDPA regulations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">11. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            Currently, <span class="font-semibold">Nodeflux Pte. Ltd</span> does not utilize cookies, web beacons, or other tracking technologies
            on our website. Should this policy change, you will be notified and your consent will be obtained where required.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">12. Children’s Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            We do not knowingly collect, use, or disclose personal data from children under 18. If we become aware of any such data, we will
            take steps to delete it. Parents or guardians who believe their child has provided personal data without consent can contact us
            to request its deletion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">13. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            <span class="font-semibold">Nodeflux Pte. Ltd</span> reserves the right to amend or update this Privacy Policy. We recommend reviewing
            this policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your data. For material changes, we will notify you directly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">14. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            If you have any inquiries, requests, or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="text-foreground/80">
            <span class="font-semibold">Nodeflux Pte. Ltd</span><br />
            112 MIDDLE ROAD #03-01<br />
            MIDLAND HOUSE<br />
            SINGAPORE 188970<br />
            <a href="mailto:legal@nodeflux.org" class="text-blue-500 underline">legal@nodeflux.org</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
